Package: pvs-monitoring
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: dangogh <dank@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/dangogh/pvs-monitoring
Description: PVS6 solar monitor with MCP integration
 Monitors a SunPower PVS6 solar gateway via WebSocket,
 persists power readings to SQLite, and exposes data
 via MCP tools for use with Claude Desktop.
 .
 Includes systemd services for pvs-monitor, pvs-api, and pvs-ui.
